   <p>The report of the yearly meeting of Orphan Home is more complete this year than ever.</p>
   <p>The society has had, in 1909, twelve regular meetings and two special meetings.</p>
   <p>Sixty-three new members for 1909 make a total of 441 members in good standing.</p>
   <p>We have many members who have fallen behind in their dues, because we have neglected to visit them and keep up their interest in the society.</p>
